data.meta_description: Felicia Farr was born on October 4, 1932 in Westchester County, New York, USA as Olive Felicia Dines. She is an actress, known for Charley Varrick (1973), 3:10 to Yuma (1957) and Kiss Me, Stupid (1964). She was previously married to Jack Lemmon and Lee Farr.
